16:08.101 --> 16:12.138
How long after this incident
did you call the police?

16:12.172 --> 16:13.740
Three days.

16:13.774 --> 16:15.408
Three days?

16:15.441 --> 16:17.243
I was confused.

16:17.277 --> 16:19.279
Confused about
whether you'd been raped?

16:19.312 --> 16:20.380
I wasn't --

16:20.413 --> 16:22.148
