16:22.182 --> 16:24.651
I needed
to talk to someone,

16:24.685 --> 16:26.520
so I went
to the rape crisis center

16:26.553 --> 16:28.388
to talk to a counselor.

16:28.421 --> 16:33.126
You met
with a rape counselor?

16:33.159 --> 16:36.162
Yes, at the Boston
Crisis Center.

16:38.098 --> 16:40.400
Do you remember
the counselor's name?

16:40.433 --> 16:44.337
Yeah -- Lucy Hatcher.
She's right there.

16:48.609 --> 16:51.645
What did you tell
Ms. Hatcher?

16:51.678 --> 16:52.713
Objection.
Privilege.

16:52.746 --> 16:54.515
Sustained.

16:54.548 --> 16:58.151
Did you become clear
that you'd been raped

16:58.184 --> 17:01.154
after talking
to this counselor?

17:01.187 --> 17:03.123
Yes.

17:03.156 --> 17:05.391
After meeting
with this counselor,

17:05.425 --> 17:08.228
