to call the police?

17:08.261 --> 17:10.329
Yes.

17:17.771 --> 17:19.673
I'm an American.

17:19.705 --> 17:21.107
You were born
in this country?

17:21.141 --> 17:22.407
No, but --

17:22.442 --> 17:24.176
I adopted Manny when
