17:24.210 --> 17:26.412
He was my sister's boy.

17:26.445 --> 17:29.315
She came here from Colombia
to get her green card.

17:29.349 --> 17:31.217
She was only here
for a month

17:31.251 --> 17:33.453
when she was killed
in a car accident.

17:33.486 --> 17:35.355
You legally adopted him?

17:35.388 --> 17:37.658
Yes. I have
all the court papers.

17:37.691 --> 17:40.861
Did you file papers
with the immigration service?

17:40.894 --> 17:45.131
Nobody advised me
I-I had to do that.

17:45.165 --> 17:46.600
Okay.

17:46.633 --> 17:49.335
Technically, Manny isn't
