17:49.369 --> 17:50.771
-What?
-HECTOR: Why?

17:50.804 --> 17:52.839
You're not a U. S. citizen,
and because you have

17:52.873 --> 17:54.675
a felony drug conviction
on your record,

17:54.708 --> 17:56.610
the I. N. S. Has the power
to remove you.

17:56.643 --> 17:59.580
They want to send you
back to Colombia.

17:59.613 --> 18:01.181
Back to Colombia?

18:01.214 --> 18:02.849
He doesn't even
know anyone in Colombia.

18:02.883 --> 18:04.317
We have no family there.

18:04.350 --> 18:05.852
He doesn't even
speak Spanish.

18:05.886 --> 18:08.288
Something is going on here.
I don't know what, but --

18:08.321 --> 18:10.791
The drug conviction
was over a year ago.

18:10.824 --> 18:13.293
Why do they want
to deport him now?

18:16.429 --> 18:18.899
I thought she wanted
to have sex.

18:18.932 --> 18:20.834
She said that
she pushed you off.

18:20.867 --> 18:22.536
