18:23.604 --> 18:25.639
Did she tell you
to stop?

18:25.672 --> 18:26.907
She said no
a couple times, but --

18:26.940 --> 18:28.241
But what?

18:28.274 --> 18:31.311
It wasn't "no"
like "don't."

18:31.344 --> 18:34.915
It was more "no" like
"we shouldn't be doing this."

18:34.948 --> 18:37.818
What was the difference
in your mind?

18:37.851 --> 18:40.220
Well, we weren't
even on a date.

18:40.253 --> 18:41.922
We had just met
at a party,

18:41.955 --> 18:43.790
and I was
walking her home.

18:43.824 --> 18:44.925
She didn't --

18:44.958 --> 18:46.860
I felt
she wanted to have sex,

18:46.893 --> 18:48.929
but was conflicted
about it --

18:48.962 --> 18:50.764
about seeming
promiscuous.

18:50.797 --> 18:52.633
Did you force yourself
on her?

18:52.666 --> 18:53.734
No.

18:53.767 --> 18:55.368
I definitely
took the initiative,

18:55.401 --> 18:58.438
but I thought I was doing
something we both wanted.

18:58.471 --> 19:00.340
Now, after you had sex,
Mr. Smith,

19:00.373 --> 19:01.341
then what happened?

19:01.374 --> 19:03.343
We shared a ginger ale,

19:03.376 --> 19:05.445
we talked for a while,
and then I left.

19:05.478 --> 19:07.681
Was she crying or...

19:07.714 --> 19:08.649
No.

19:08.682 --> 19:10.250
Did she seem upset?

19:10.283 --> 19:11.351
No.

19:11.384 --> 19:13.820
I mean, she did
have some regret, but --

19:13.854 --> 19:14.921
What kind of regret?

19:14.955 --> 19:16.289
Well,
she just kept saying

19:16.322 --> 19:17.390
we really shouldn't
have done that,

19:17.423 --> 19:18.625
and that she's not
the type of girl

19:18.659 --> 19:20.193
who meets a man
and has sex,

19:20.226 --> 19:23.697
but she wasn't
angry at me.

19:23.730 --> 19:26.533
She seemed to be
more angry at herself.

19:26.567 --> 19:29.570
HELEN: Did she rip
her own clothes?

19:29.603 --> 19:31.437
No, I probably did that.

19:31.471 --> 19:33.540
What about the bruise
on her left wrist?

19:33.574 --> 19:34.808
If I did that,

19:34.841 --> 19:36.643
