I was hurting her.

19:36.677 --> 19:40.413
So when she said no,

19:40.446 --> 19:42.448
you figured
she didn't really mean it,

19:42.482 --> 19:44.518
and therefore,
you took the initiative?

19:44.551 --> 19:46.920
I guess that's right.

19:46.953 --> 19:50.757
So you bruised her wrist,
you tore her clothes off,

19:50.791 --> 19:52.458
she told you to stop,

19:52.492 --> 19:53.760
but in your mind,

19:53.794 --> 19:56.362
you figured
she really wanted it.

19:56.396 --> 19:58.832
Yes. A lot of women,

19:58.865 --> 20:00.000
they don't want to be
thought of as promiscuous,

20:00.033 --> 20:01.835
so they'll resist
a little,

20:01.868 --> 20:04.304
even though they really
want you to keep going.

20:04.337 --> 20:06.540
I see.

20:06.573 --> 20:08.775
I think we can end
with that answer.

20:08.809 --> 20:10.476
Nothing further.

20:10.511 --> 20:13.346
The witness may step down.

20:15.916 --> 20:17.751
Your Honor, at this time,

20:17.784 --> 20:20.253
