Lucy Hatcher to the stand.

20:20.286 --> 20:22.856
Objection. This witness has
no competence or foundation --

20:22.889 --> 20:24.858
This witness
was the turning point

20:24.891 --> 20:26.359
is Ms. Danzer's decision

20:26.392 --> 20:28.294
to falsely accuse
my client of rape,

20:28.328 --> 20:30.664
and I would like
to cross-examine her.

20:30.697 --> 20:31.732
Any communication
between Ms. Danzer

20:31.765 --> 20:32.966
and her counselor
is privileged.

20:32.999 --> 20:34.367
That privilege is outweighed

20:34.400 --> 20:35.769
by the defendant's right
to a fair trial.

20:35.802 --> 20:38.371
Only if Ms. Hatcher is aware
of exculpatory evidence.

20:38.404 --> 20:39.840
That's not the case here.

20:39.873 --> 20:41.908
Your Honor, that's exactly
what I'm looking to find out.

20:41.942 --> 20:43.009
This is a criminal trial.

20:43.043 --> 20:45.912
My client
faces serious charges.

20:45.946 --> 20:48.414
I should be allowed
to explore this issue.

20:50.684 --> 20:53.687
I'll see Ms. Hatcher
in chambers tomorrow morning.

21:11.371 --> 21:13.840
Okay...

21:13.874 --> 21:15.709
you were trying to tell me
something last night.

21:15.742 --> 21:19.279
I can't really talk
on the record, Lindsay.

21:21.481 --> 21:22.649
Off the record...

21:22.683 --> 21:25.519
if you'd like
to have a seat...

21:34.427 --> 21:37.731
Six weeks ago, an undercover
narcotics officer

21:37.764 --> 21:41.735
was shot and killed
in the backroom
of a Lawrence bar.

21:41.768 --> 21:43.436
Your client was there.

21:43.469 --> 21:45.939
Was he involved?

21:45.972 --> 21:47.708
I don't think so,

21:47.741 --> 21:49.776
but he saw who did it.

21:49.810 --> 21:52.445
The police believe
it was somebody

21:52.478 --> 21:55.849
Manny used to run with
during his drug days.

21:55.882 --> 21:59.085
Basically, your client's
a material witness

21:59.119 --> 22:00.654
who's not talking.

22:00.687 --> 22:03.657
So this is leverage.

22:03.690 --> 22:06.993
Seems so.

22:08.829 --> 22:10.697
And those drugs
were planted in his car

22:10.731 --> 22:12.766
to get leverage.

22:12.799 --> 22:15.636
That I don't know.
All I can say, Lindsay --

22:15.669 --> 22:18.438
The police are on a mission
to get the killer.

22:18.471 --> 22:20.507
Your guy
is caught in the middle.

22:20.541 --> 22:23.744
This is extortion.

22:23.777 --> 22:25.846
All the charges
are legitimate.

22:25.879 --> 22:28.815
The motive for bringing them
isn't really relevant.

22:31.017 --> 22:33.787
That's why I wanted
to settle this quickly,

22:33.820 --> 22:36.122
before all this stuff
went into motion.

22:36.156 --> 22:37.991
I can't really
interfere now.

22:38.024 --> 22:39.826
What's the offer?

22:39.860 --> 22:41.795
If he credibly
I. D. s the shooter,

22:41.828 --> 22:43.564
Manny will get
an "S" visa.

22:43.597 --> 22:45.799
He can stay in the country
indefinitely.

22:45.832 --> 22:47.934
What if he doesn't know
who the shooter is?

22:47.968 --> 22:51.471
He's got a problem.

23:01.848 --> 23:03.584
If rape counselors
can be forced to testify,

23:03.617 --> 23:05.118
what good will they be?

23:05.151 --> 23:07.187
-Perhaps not as --
