to talk to me.

23:07.220 --> 23:08.855
I just need to know
the details

23:08.889 --> 23:10.524
of your first conversation

23:10.557 --> 23:12.158
so I can make a determination
as to whether --

23:12.192 --> 23:13.794
Why?

23:13.827 --> 23:19.099
How did you help her
decide she had been raped?

23:19.132 --> 23:21.835
That's privilege.

23:26.139 --> 23:28.742
I'm overriding
that privilege.

23:28.775 --> 23:30.511
What?

23:30.544 --> 23:32.646
I'm allowing
your testimony.

23:36.482 --> 23:38.719
I asked you if there
was something you knew
that I didn't.

23:38.752 --> 23:40.754
I didn't know that had
anything to do with this.

23:40.787 --> 23:43.690
-If you saw --
-I didn't. I was there,
I didn't see anything.

23:43.724 --> 23:46.026
Manny, this is not the time
to cover for a friend.

23:46.059 --> 23:48.461
I'm not.

23:48.494 --> 23:50.664
How can they
just do this?

23:50.697 --> 23:53.099
They're the I. N. S.
With a felony conviction,

23:53.133 --> 23:55.836
