a noncitizen, which you are.

23:55.869 --> 23:58.138
You will be gone.

23:58.171 --> 24:02.643
I can't prevent that.

24:02.676 --> 24:07.781
They're offering you
a visa if you cooperate.

24:07.814 --> 24:09.816
You saw it.

24:14.087 --> 24:16.623
Tell me.

24:18.959 --> 24:20.561
I can't.

24:20.594 --> 24:22.128
Manny, you're about
to be deported

24:22.162 --> 24:24.230
to a country where
you don't know anybody.

24:24.264 --> 24:26.667
The only person that can
help you here is you.

24:28.101 --> 24:30.871
This is
lawyer/client, right?

24:30.904 --> 24:32.105
Of course.

24:32.138 --> 24:35.642
You can't repeat nothing --
Not to anyone.

24:35.676 --> 24:37.978
Of course not.

24:40.614 --> 24:42.783
It was my brother.

24:44.918 --> 24:46.587
What?

24:48.755 --> 24:51.091
Your brother
was the shooter?

24:51.124 --> 24:53.259
