more seriously.

25:21.955 --> 25:23.990
You can just sit there
quiet.

25:24.024 --> 25:25.926
Look, I do have
work to do.

25:25.959 --> 25:27.293
They're due here
any second.

25:27.327 --> 25:31.598
The meeting should take
a half-hour, tops.

25:31.632 --> 25:32.899
Do you have
a squeal number?

25:32.933 --> 25:34.100
A what?

25:34.134 --> 25:36.269
A squeal number --
A number you'll take.

25:36.302 --> 25:38.271
Well, six figures
would be good.

25:38.304 --> 25:40.240
Listen, Eugene,
it's probably best

25:40.273 --> 25:42.175
