the meeting.

25:42.208 --> 25:43.343
Lead the meeting?

25:43.376 --> 25:44.978
Just start things off.

25:45.011 --> 25:47.814
You know, how your firm is
prepared to try this case --

25:47.848 --> 25:49.850
