be trying it,

25:54.688 --> 25:55.989
and if you think
for a second --

25:56.022 --> 25:57.958
Uh, gentlemen.
Come right in.

25:57.991 --> 26:00.861
We're all ready
for you.

26:00.894 --> 26:03.163
That's John Rapherson.

26:03.196 --> 26:06.266
You know him?

26:06.299 --> 26:07.968
Do I know him?

26:10.403 --> 26:12.973
Mr. Bassett.

26:13.006 --> 26:15.609
Mr. Bassett.

26:15.642 --> 26:17.878
I did not convince Meredith
she had been raped.

26:17.911 --> 26:19.880
