a rape crisis counselor,

27:01.221 --> 27:02.422
and that I had --

27:02.455 --> 27:04.224
Is it your testimony,
Ms. Hatcher,

27:04.257 --> 27:06.126
that Ms. Danzer came
to the conclusion

27:06.159 --> 27:07.293
that she was raped

27:07.327 --> 27:08.862
independently
of your influence?

27:08.895 --> 27:11.197
I can't really
know that, Mr. Tager.

27:11.231 --> 27:13.199
-Well, could she have?
-The witness has answered
she doesn't know.

27:13.233 --> 27:14.334
Withdrawn.

27:14.367 --> 27:16.970
When a person
is sexually assaulted,

27:17.003 --> 27:19.806
is this something
that she gets over easily

27:19.840 --> 27:20.941
with counseling?

27:20.974 --> 27:22.342
Of course not.

27:22.375 --> 27:24.244
In fact,
some of these victims

27:24.277 --> 27:26.813
carry the trauma with them
for a long time, do they not?

27:26.847 --> 27:28.949
Some the rest
of their lives.

27:28.982 --> 27:30.216
Many are angry.

27:30.250 --> 27:32.018
Would that be consistent
with your testimony?

27:32.052 --> 27:33.954
Yes.

27:33.987 --> 27:35.221
Have you ever been
sexually assaulted,

27:35.255 --> 27:36.256
Ms. Hatcher?

27:36.289 --> 27:37.991
HELEN: Objection.

27:38.024 --> 27:40.426
Goes to bias,
your honor.

27:40.460 --> 27:43.163
I'll allow it.

27:47.968 --> 27:50.270
Have you ever been
sexually assaulted?

27:58.779 --> 28:00.280
Yes.

28:00.313 --> 28:02.282
Your dentist
molested you

28:02.315 --> 28:04.851
while you were
under anesthesia.

28:04.885 --> 28:07.020
Yes.

28:07.053 --> 28:09.089
And the superintendent
at your apartment

28:09.122 --> 28:11.925
secretly installed cameras,
and he photographed you.

28:11.958 --> 28:13.426
Your honor, this has
no probative value.

28:13.459 --> 28:15.261
I'm allowing it,
Ms. Gamble.

28:15.295 --> 28:16.830
Please sit down.

28:16.863 --> 28:18.832
Truthfully, Ms. Hatcher,

28:18.865 --> 28:21.234
when you decided to become
a rape crisis counselor,

28:21.267 --> 28:24.505
is it possible that
your own anger was in play?

28:24.538 --> 28:26.740
