to do with that.

28:26.773 --> 28:28.074
Nothing at all?

28:28.108 --> 28:29.876
No.

28:40.921 --> 28:42.789
You've seen
the discovery.

28:42.823 --> 28:45.526
The doctors have cited
Reflexin as the cause.

28:45.559 --> 28:48.261
Look, I'm not a scientist.
None of us is here,

28:48.294 --> 28:50.163
so it wouldn't make
much sense

28:50.196 --> 28:51.965
for us to debate
liability.

28:51.998 --> 28:55.368
Our client has directed us
not to settle.

28:55.401 --> 28:58.972
I suspect your client
doesn't really want a trial.

28:59.005 --> 29:01.074
Actually, Mr. Young,
in this case, they do.

29:01.107 --> 29:03.510
There's nothing better
than a trial sometimes

29:03.544 --> 29:05.946
to send the message
that you won't settle out,

29:05.979 --> 29:07.447
and this one presents

29:07.480 --> 29:10.851
a pretty risk-free
opportunity in their minds.

29:10.884 --> 29:12.218
You're here.

29:12.252 --> 29:14.154
Obviously,
you've got a number.

29:14.187 --> 29:18.324
Well, the number,
I'm afraid, is zero.

29:18.358 --> 29:22.295
We're here to satisfy ourselves
that it's the correct number.

29:22.328 --> 29:24.798
We just beat the EPA
for over $30 million

29:24.831 --> 29:26.967
on injuries that weren't
even as bad.

29:27.000 --> 29:28.535
They beat the EPA,
Mr. Bassett.

29:28.569 --> 29:31.237
Now, while I salute
your last-minute ingenuity

29:31.271 --> 29:33.840
in signing them up
for shock value,

29:33.874 --> 29:36.376
we know who opposing counsel
really is.

29:36.409 --> 29:39.980
My firm is very prepared
to be involved here.

29:40.013 --> 29:42.415
This is complex
product liability,

29:42.448 --> 29:45.118
and however impressive
your talent,

29:45.151 --> 29:48.254
there's no way you could
conceivably be ready

29:48.288 --> 29:50.256
to try this
by next week.

29:50.290 --> 29:52.258
Mr. Bassett will have to
lead this charge,

29:52.292 --> 29:53.960
whether he wants to
or not.

29:53.994 --> 29:54.995
We'll get a continuance.

29:55.028 --> 29:57.130
He's gotten six of them.

29:57.163 --> 30:01.201
The judge indicated
this last one was final.

30:01.234 --> 30:02.402
We're very sorry

30:02.435 --> 30:04.404
for the young girl's
difficulties,

30:04.437 --> 30:09.275
but we maintain our client
did not cause them.

30:09.309 --> 30:13.146
Thank you for agreeing
to meet with us.

30:22.022 --> 30:25.025
The man who just walked
out of this room

30:25.058 --> 30:29.996
is one of the top three
civil litigators in Boston.

30:32.198 --> 30:35.301
Are you ready to try
this case against him?

30:40.340 --> 30:44.177
How can they just remove
a person from a country?

30:44.210 --> 30:47.413
Just because I forgot to file
some adoption papers?

30:47.447 --> 30:51.117
They're convinced he knows
who shot this police officer.

30:51.151 --> 30:53.086
And what did he say?

30:53.119 --> 30:55.355
He says he didn't
see anything.

30:57.591 --> 30:59.526
Can't you go to federal court
and try to undo this?

30:59.560 --> 31:01.494
I'm going in this afternoon.

31:01.528 --> 31:04.531
I've scheduled a hearing
with the judge.

31:04.565 --> 31:07.333
But if I lose that,
they'll take him.

31:07.367 --> 31:10.170
He'll be on a plane
to Colombia.

31:10.203 --> 31:13.306
If he did see something,
maybe you two

31:13.339 --> 31:17.310
can convince him
to reveal what he can.

31:17.343 --> 31:19.913
It may be his only chance.

31:19.946 --> 31:22.616
We'll talk to him.

31:22.649 --> 31:26.319
I appreciate that.

31:26.352 --> 31:28.589
I'd gone to the hospital
because I had bruising.

31:28.622 --> 31:31.324
-From?
-Having sex.

31:31.357 --> 31:33.359
And the doctor
who treated me,

31:33.393 --> 31:36.597
I guess he was concerned
that maybe I'd been assaulted.

31:36.630 --> 31:39.065
-Had you been?
-No.

31:39.099 --> 31:41.301
I guess it was pretty rough,

31:41.334 --> 31:44.070
but it was
totally consensual.

31:44.104 --> 31:46.139
Did you talk
to Lucy Hatcher?

31:46.172 --> 31:47.473
Yes.

31:47.508 --> 31:49.576
And did you tell her
that the sex was consensual?

31:49.610 --> 31:53.046
-Yes.
-And how did she respond?

31:53.079 --> 31:55.215
She tried to convince me
that I'd been raped.

31:55.248 --> 31:56.617
She wanted
to call the cops.

31:56.650 --> 31:58.585
I kept telling her
it wasn't a rape,

31:58.619 --> 32:00.954
but she just didn't want
to accept that.

32:00.987 --> 32:02.656
Thank you, Cindy.

32:02.689 --> 32:04.591
Yours.

32:06.492 --> 32:10.296
Have you ever needed
to be hospitalized

32:10.330 --> 32:12.966
after having
consensual sex before?

32:12.999 --> 32:14.635
No.

32:14.668 --> 32:19.506
You filed
a police report, didn't you?

32:19.540 --> 32:22.342
Only because Lucy Hatcher
convinced me to.

32:22.375 --> 32:24.310
She's the one
who pushed it.

32:24.344 --> 32:25.712
The rape counselor,

32:25.746 --> 32:27.480
the woman who you
voluntarily talked to

32:27.514 --> 32:29.282
about what happened
that night...

32:29.315 --> 32:30.350
I wasn't raped.

32:30.383 --> 32:31.518
Yet when a doctor
asked you

32:31.552 --> 32:32.553
if you wanted to see
a rape counselor,

32:32.586 --> 32:34.655
you said yes,
didn't you?

32:34.688 --> 32:36.690
Yes.

32:36.723 --> 32:40.160
Nothing further.

32:40.193 --> 32:42.328
JUDGE: The witness
may step down.

32:45.231 --> 32:47.433
She was raped, Helen.

32:47.467 --> 32:48.769
It was total date rape.

32:48.802 --> 32:51.705
Either she's too ashamed
or she's in denial.

32:51.738 --> 32:54.374
I never convinced her
to file a report.

32:54.407 --> 32:55.676
All right, Lucy.

32:55.709 --> 32:57.477
Can't you put me back
up there to impeach her?

32:57.511 --> 32:59.713
It won't do us any good.

33:13.326 --> 33:16.262
The movers will pick up
the files by 3:00.

33:16.296 --> 33:18.632
Okay.

33:18.665 --> 33:21.334
I could sure use
a second chair at the trial

33:21.367 --> 33:22.736
if you're interested.

33:22.769 --> 33:27.107
Harland, I don't know
that I'd do you much good.

33:27.140 --> 33:29.342
I could get you
up to speed.

33:29.375 --> 33:31.645
I just can't.

33:31.678 --> 33:33.213
Sorry.

33:33.246 --> 33:36.149
Yeah.

33:36.182 --> 33:38.752
Uh, anyway,
I-I hope you don't mind,

33:38.785 --> 33:40.821
I scheduled a meeting here
with the client.

33:40.854 --> 33:42.723
I didn't know how long
we'd be tied up

33:42.756 --> 33:44.725
trying to settle.
If I could just

33:44.758 --> 33:46.326
borrow the conference room

33:46.359 --> 33:49.530
for another half-hour
or so...

33:55.301 --> 33:57.170
Sure.

33:59.205 --> 34:02.676
Three days later
she cries rape,

34:02.709 --> 34:05.679
after meeting
with this Lucy Hatcher,

34:05.712 --> 34:08.281
who convinced her
to cry rape,

34:08.313 --> 34:12.152
a rape counselor who had
been victimized herself,

34:12.185 --> 34:14.353
who admitted herself
that she didn't know

34:14.387 --> 34:16.089
whether she influenced

34:16.121 --> 34:19.659
Meredith Danzer's decision
to call the police or not.

34:19.693 --> 34:22.563
Meredith told you that
prior to her meeting

34:22.596 --> 34:25.565
with Ms. Hatcher,
she was confused

34:25.599 --> 34:28.501
about whether
she had been raped.

34:28.534 --> 34:31.304
If the so-called victim
is confused,

34:31.337 --> 34:32.773
ladies and gentlemen,

34:32.806 --> 34:35.609
of course you have
reasonable doubt.

34:37.143 --> 34:40.213
Meredith sought out
a rape counselor.

34:40.246 --> 34:43.283
Lucy Hatcher
didn't go to her.

34:43.315 --> 34:45.851
Her wrists were bruised.

34:45.886 --> 34:48.722
Her clothes were ripped.

34:48.755 --> 34:50.290
She said no.

34:50.322 --> 34:53.393
She tried to push
Benjamin Smith off.

34:53.426 --> 34:55.829
He pinned her legs
with his knees

34:55.862 --> 34:57.764
and forced himself in her.

34:57.798 --> 35:00.767
That is rape,
ladies and gentlemen.

35:00.801 --> 35:04.304
It doesn't matter how many
days later it is reported.

35:04.337 --> 35:09.610
Nonconsensual sex by force
is rape.

35:09.643 --> 35:11.778
All these cases
involve discretion,

35:11.812 --> 35:13.213
and it's an abuse,

35:13.246 --> 35:14.447
Throwing this kid
out of the country

35:14.480 --> 35:15.849
on a year-old
drug conviction.

35:15.882 --> 35:17.651
You know we have authority
on this matter, Ms. Dole.

35:17.684 --> 35:20.220
I'm not challenging
your authority.

35:20.253 --> 35:21.888
He was adopted
at the age of one.

35:21.922 --> 35:23.757
He's not from a foreign nation.
He's from here.

35:23.790 --> 35:26.627
It doesn't quite smell right,
I grant you,

35:26.660 --> 35:29.329
but the discretion
you speak of, Ms. Dole,

35:29.362 --> 35:30.496
is very wide.

35:30.531 --> 35:32.599
They're using this
to extort testimony.

35:32.633 --> 35:34.400
You cannot leverage
deportation.

35:34.434 --> 35:36.903
Whatever this country
is about, it can't be that.

35:36.937 --> 35:38.772
Don't run him up the flagpole
as a model citizen.

35:38.805 --> 35:40.841
Well, he pretty much
is a model citizen.

35:40.874 --> 35:42.776
Then he should perform
his civic duty

35:42.809 --> 35:44.244
and tell the government
who killed the police officer.

35:44.277 --> 35:45.779
You don't know
that he saw anything.

35:45.812 --> 35:47.347
He was in
a 12x20-foot room.

35:47.380 --> 35:48.715
But that doesn't mean
that he saw any--

35:48.749 --> 35:50.216
If you're gonna be
disingenuous, don't cry foul.

35:50.250 --> 35:52.519
All right.

35:52.553 --> 35:54.521
I'm not going
to deny the removal petition.

35:54.555 --> 35:56.389
Your honor, please.

35:56.422 --> 35:58.491
It sounds to me
like your client's fate

35:58.525 --> 36:00.761
is in his own hands,
counsel.

36:00.794 --> 36:04.364
Get him to accept
their offer.

36:04.397 --> 36:06.900
Being in Colombia,

36:06.933 --> 36:09.536
it's better
than Hector doing life.

36:09.570 --> 36:11.237
What will you do there?

36:11.271 --> 36:14.675
No family, no friends.
You can't even speak Spanish.

36:14.708 --> 36:16.677
And, Manny,
understand this --

36:16.710 --> 36:19.379
You can never come back here,
not even on a tourist visa.

36:19.412 --> 36:21.281
Maybe I can sneak back in.

36:21.314 --> 36:23.283
And if you're caught doing that,
you could get 20 years,

36:23.316 --> 36:24.718
after which
they'll deport you again.

36:24.751 --> 36:27.554
I know you love
your brother very much,

36:27.588 --> 36:30.390
but this is too big
a sacrifice.

36:30.423 --> 36:33.527
My advice,

36:33.560 --> 36:35.295
tell the police
what you know.

36:35.328 --> 36:36.296
I can't.

36:36.329 --> 36:38.431
It would kill my mother.

36:38.464 --> 36:39.966
Losing you will hurt
your mother more than --

36:40.000 --> 36:42.268
You don't understand.

36:44.905 --> 36:48.575
It would kill my mother.

36:50.777 --> 36:52.613
What are you talking about?

36:52.646 --> 36:56.617
Hector says if I tell,

36:56.650 --> 36:59.419
he'll have her killed.

37:01.755 --> 37:03.456
And he'd do it, Ms. Dole.

37:03.489 --> 37:05.992
You don't know how ruthless
he can be.

37:06.026 --> 37:09.462
Your brother would --
would kill your mother,

37:09.495 --> 37:10.731
his mother if --

37:10.764 --> 37:13.433
He says he would.

37:13.466 --> 37:17.051
And from what I know
and from what I've seen...

37:20.373 --> 37:22.909
I'm not sure he wouldn't.

37:35.055 --> 37:37.524
JUDGE: Will the defendant
please rise?

37:43.063 --> 37:45.799
Madame foreperson,
has the jury reached a verdict?

37:45.832 --> 37:47.768
We have, your honor.

37:47.801 --> 37:50.937
What say you?

37:50.971 --> 37:53.840
Commonwealth vs. Smith
on the charge of rape,

37:53.874 --> 37:55.576
we find the defendant
Benjamin Smith

37:55.609 --> 37:57.043
not guilty.

37:57.077 --> 37:59.880
JUDGE: Members of the jury,
this completes your service.

37:59.913 --> 38:02.783
You are dismissed
with the thanks of the court.

38:02.816 --> 38:05.451
The defendant is free to go.
We're adjourned.

38:05.485 --> 38:07.921
(judge pounds gavel)

38:16.429 --> 38:18.331
I'm sorry.

38:18.364 --> 38:19.733
You did your best.

38:19.766 --> 38:21.735
And so did you, Meredith.

38:21.768 --> 38:24.671
You were very courageous
coming in here.

38:24.705 --> 38:26.406
Thank you.

38:26.439 --> 38:28.842
If there's any way
I can help you...

38:28.875 --> 38:30.711
Thanks.

38:30.744 --> 38:33.947
I'd better go.

38:50.063 --> 38:53.634
I never told her to lie
or say anything --

38:53.667 --> 38:55.101
I know you didn't.

38:55.135 --> 39:00.473
I don't think
I steered her.

39:00.507 --> 39:01.875
I don't think I did.

39:01.908 --> 39:05.411
I'm sure you didn't mean to
if you did.

39:05.445 --> 39:09.750
But if you did...

39:09.783 --> 39:13.486
It's the toughest part
of my job, Luce,

39:13.520 --> 39:17.123
and I make up my mind
what the right result should be,

39:17.157 --> 39:19.660
and I'm tempted to steer
my witnesses

39:19.693 --> 39:21.662
to accomplish that result.

39:23.697 --> 39:27.100
It's the toughest part of my job
to resist that.

39:29.102 --> 39:32.939
It might be a difficult thing
for you in your job, too.

39:45.552 --> 39:47.654
Oh. May I help you?

39:47.688 --> 39:50.657
I'm looking
for Harland Bassett.

39:50.691 --> 39:53.860
Oh, Christine, hello.

39:53.894 --> 39:55.461
Hi, Annie.

39:55.495 --> 39:57.197
How'd we do?

39:57.230 --> 40:00.567
Well, didn't get the number
I want yet.

40:00.601 --> 40:02.068
Um, Eugene,

40:02.102 --> 40:04.938
this is Christine
and Annie Mullin, our clients.

40:04.971 --> 40:06.439
Hello.

40:07.574 --> 40:10.210
Hi, Annie.
I'm Eugene Young.

40:10.243 --> 40:12.012
Hello.

40:12.045 --> 40:13.547
How you doing?

40:13.580 --> 40:15.916
I'm fine.

40:15.949 --> 40:17.784
What did we get?

40:17.818 --> 40:21.454
Well, they didn't want
to settle at all.

40:22.623 --> 40:25.759
What does that mean?

40:25.792 --> 40:30.664
It means, sweetie,
we're going to go to trial.

40:30.697 --> 40:32.999
And you're going to beat them?

40:33.033 --> 40:37.504
Well, it'll be tough,

40:37.538 --> 40:39.506
but, uh, you know...

40:39.540 --> 40:42.208
We're going to try, Annie.

40:42.242 --> 40:45.445
Harland.

40:51.184 --> 40:53.186
That drug did this to her?

40:53.219 --> 40:54.621
Every bit of it.

40:54.655 --> 40:57.490
Six months ago
she was completely healthy.

41:00.160 --> 41:02.162
Get your files
back into that room.

41:02.195 --> 41:04.631
Yes, sir.

41:09.202 --> 41:11.772
Annie...

41:11.805 --> 41:14.575
you up for a fight?

41:14.608 --> 41:17.277
Yes.

41:17.310 --> 41:20.046
You tough enough to
take on the drug company?

41:21.314 --> 41:23.917
I'll be as tough
as I need to be.

41:27.821 --> 41:30.691
That's what I want to hear?

41:34.027 --> 41:37.531
Is there any way
to reverse it?

41:37.564 --> 41:40.567
I don't think so.
I'll keep trying.

41:40.601 --> 41:43.604
When would he be deported?

41:43.637 --> 41:46.272
A week, maybe two.

41:50.076 --> 41:52.679
When my sister died,

41:52.713 --> 41:57.918
I promised myself
I would take care of him,

41:57.951 --> 42:01.755
that I would love him
as my own.

42:03.957 --> 42:06.760
Well, you've certainly
done that.

42:09.229 --> 42:12.999
I'd appreciate it
if you would keep working.

42:13.033 --> 42:14.635
Whatever...

42:14.668 --> 42:16.703
Okay.

42:21.875 --> 42:24.978
I'm sorry, Mrs. Guzman.

42:27.313 --> 42:28.782
Yeah.

42:33.319 --> 42:35.155
Good night.

42:58.378 --> 42:59.913
I heard.

42:59.946 --> 43:03.183
I just came from Manny.

43:03.216 --> 43:05.986
Thanks for everything
you did.

43:07.888 --> 43:09.055
Sure.

